+------------------------------------------------------------------------
+Meanwhile, in the earlier versions, you would see a message like:
+------------------------------------------------------------------------
     hda_codec: Unknown model for ALC880, trying auto-probe from BIOS...
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Even if you see such a message, DON'T PANIC.  Take a deep breath and
